724
00:39:42,720 --> 00:39:44,000
Mesti memberi perhatian kepada pengelupasan.

725
00:39:44,660 --> 00:39:47,740
Kemudian, air renyah, intipati, sapu dengan panas.

726
00:39:48,120 --> 00:39:49,360
Kalau rumah kamu ada alat,

727
00:39:49,390 --> 00:39:51,470
